    public class SLAEventKafkaJobMonitor
extends KafkaAvroJobMonitor<GobblinTrackingEvent>
    A KafkaJobMonitor that parses SLA GobblinTrackingEvents and generates JobSpecs. Used to trigger jobs on data availability.
